snippet.title: Scary World Trailer
snippet.description:
You are about to see a scary world. Can you discover its secret?

SCARY WORLD is a new BULLET-HEAVEN ROGUELIKE, kind of like Vampire Survivors, but with physics, and the matches are only 10 minutes long instead of 30. Also it has different unique powers, some of which take your physics into account like the lance, which does more damage the faster you're moving. There are speed boosts, land mines, many different characters to unlock, and huge scary bosses.

Coming to Steam and itch.io soon!

Learn more at www.keithburgun.net
